## Common Patterns

### Loading States

```tsx
export const Loading: Story = {
  args: {
    isLoading: true,
    children: "Loading...",
  },
};
```

### Error States

```tsx
export const Error: Story = {
  args: {
    variant: "destructive",
    children: "Error: Failed to load",
  },
};
```

### Empty States

```tsx
export const Empty: Story = {
  render: () => (
    <EmptyState
      illustration={<SearchIcon className="h-30 w-30" />}
      title="No results found"
      description="Try adjusting your search terms"
    />
  ),
};
```

### Long Content

```tsx
export const LongText: Story = {
  args: {
    children: "This is a very long button text that might wrap to multiple lines",
  },
};
```

## Accessibility Testing

### ARIA Attributes

```tsx
export const AccessibleButton: Story = {
  args: {
    "aria-label": "Close modal",
    children: <XIcon />,
  },
};
```

### Keyboard Navigation

Document keyboard support in story description:

```tsx
export const Default: Story = {
  parameters: {
    docs: {
      description: {
        story: `
**Keyboard support:**
- \`Tab\`: Focus the button
- \`Enter\` or \`Space\`: Activate the button
        `,
      },
    },
  },
};
```

## Common Mistakes

### Mistake: No Playground Story

```tsx
// ❌ BAD - No interactive playground
export const Primary: Story = { args: { variant: "primary" } };
export const Secondary: Story = { args: { variant: "secondary" } };

// ✅ GOOD - Includes playground
export const Primary: Story = { /* ... */ };
export const Secondary: Story = { /* ... */ };
export const Playground: Story = { 
  args: { variant: "primary", size: "md" }
};
```

### Mistake: Missing ArgTypes

```tsx
// ❌ BAD - No control descriptions
argTypes: {
  variant: {
    control: "select",
    options: ["primary", "secondary"],
  },
}

// ✅ GOOD - Includes descriptions
argTypes: {
  variant: {
    control: "select",
    options: ["primary", "secondary"],
    description: "The visual style variant of the button",
  },
}
```

### Mistake: Not Using Realistic Content

```tsx
// ❌ BAD
children: "Button"
text: "Test"

// ✅ GOOD
children: "Search properties"
text: "Single Family Home"
```

### Mistake: Missing State Stories

```tsx
// ❌ BAD - Only default state
export const Default: Story = { /* ... */ };

// ✅ GOOD - Shows all states
export const Default: Story = { /* ... */ };
export const Disabled: Story = { /* ... */ };
export const Loading: Story = { /* ... */ };
export const WithIcon: Story = { /* ... */ };
```

## Must Follow

1. ✅ Create one story per variant
2. ✅ Include "AllVariants" showcase story
3. ✅ Include "Sizes" story if component has sizes
4. ✅ Include "Playground" story with all controls
5. ✅ Use realistic content, not lorem ipsum
6. ✅ Add descriptions to argTypes
7. ✅ Document keyboard support
8. ✅ Test all interactive states
9. ✅ Use `tags: ["autodocs"]` for auto-documentation
10. ✅ Co-locate story files with components
